high_descs: walk to face left side of tv bureau
pick up credit card from bureau top
walk to face blue chair in corner
put credit card on chair
walk to face couch
pick up credit card from couch
walk to face blue chair in corner
put credit card on chair

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the blue chair, the hang a right and walk over to the black table the television is on.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the black table.
Walk over to the blue chair in the corner of the room behind you.
Put the credit card on the front edge of the seat of the chair.
Walk over to the blue couch on your left.
Pick up the credit card off of the seat of the couch.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the blue chair in the corner of the room.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the right of the card that's already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a blue chair.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left of the TV stand
Grab the credit card off of the stand
Turn around and go to the couch
Put the card on the couch
Turn left and go to the middle of the sofa
Grab the credit card off of the sofa
Turn around and go to the couch
Put the card on the couch
anns.task_desc: Putting two credit cards on the couch
